        {
            "id": "https://starofeden.github.io/2023/08/17/%E4%BB%8E0%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E7%9A%84misc%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/",
            "url": "https://starofeden.github.io/2023/08/17/%E4%BB%8E0%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E7%9A%84misc%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/",
            "title": "ctfshow misc做题笔记",
            "date_published": "2023-08-16T16:00:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"pcap\"><a href=\"#pcap\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\".pcap\"></a><strong>.pcap</strong></h1><ul>\n<li>追踪TCP流<h1 id=\"图片\"><a href=\"#图片\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"图片\"></a>图片</h1></li>\n<li>先用010看看文件头：<br>（若文件头是pk则是压缩包）</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"binwalk分离文件\"><a href=\"#binwalk分离文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"binwalk分离文件\"></a>binwalk分离文件</h2><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">binwalk -e a.jpg</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li><p>若010查看文件后无头绪，可用binwalk分析，这时不用加-e</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>可能藏在属性里</p>\n<h1 id=\"dd分离\"><a href=\"#dd分离\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"dd分离\"></a>dd分离</h1><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">dd if=1.jpg of=2.jpg skip=48221 bs=1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>if 指定输入文件，of 指定输出文件，skip 指定从输入文件开头跳过 48221 个块后开始复制(binwalk第一列内容)，bs 设置每次读写块的大小为1字节</p>\n<h2 id=\"foremost\"><a href=\"#foremost\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"foremost\"></a>foremost</h2><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"压缩包\"><a href=\"#压缩包\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"压缩包\"></a>压缩包</h1><p><code>docx拖到010是以压缩包的格式来打开，可以对比压缩包头文件是否毁坏</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>编码转换 - cyberchef</p>\n</li>\n<li>循环解压</li>\n<li>暴力破解</li>\n<li>明文攻击</li>\n<li>伪加密</li>\n<li>base64加密（开头是US）<h2 id=\"密码暴力破解\"><a href=\"#密码暴力破解\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"密码暴力破解\"></a>密码暴力破解</h2><h2 id=\"可能有密文\"><a href=\"#可能有密文\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"可能有密文\"></a>可能有密文</h2></li>\n<li>所在位置：<br>图片属性</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"zip伪加密\"><a href=\"#zip伪加密\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"zip伪加密\"></a>zip伪加密</h2><p><img src=\"https://starofeden-blog.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/202403240950186.png\" alt=\"image-20240324095058093\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>识别伪加密</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://starofeden-blog.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/202403240958879.png\" alt=\"image-20240324095837812\"></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>标志位被修改</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>压缩源文件数据区：<br>          50 4B 03 04：这是头文件标记  （0x04034b50）<br>          14 00：解压文件所需 pkware 版本<br>          00 00：全局方式位标记（判断有无加密）<br>          08 00：压缩方式<br>          5A 7E：最后修改文件时间<br>          F7 46：最后修改文件日期</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p> 50 4B 01 02 1F 00 14 00 09 00 改成 50 4B 01 02 1F 00 14 00 00 00<br> <em>50 4B是PK，直接搜PK就行</em></p>\n<h1 id=\"隐写\"><a href=\"#隐写\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"隐写\"></a>隐写</h1><h2 id=\"pdf文件、有水印\"><a href=\"#pdf文件、有水印\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"pdf文件、有水印\"></a>pdf文件、有水印</h2><ul>\n<li>全选发现能选中水印，复制到记事本能看见一串密文</li>\n<li>可能是摩斯密码：A：.    B:-     空格：/<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">BABA BBB BA BBA ABA AB B AAB ABAA AB B AA BBB BA AAA BBAABB AABA ABAA AB BBA BBBAAA ABBBB BA AAAB ABBBB AAAAA ABBBB BAAA ABAA AAABB BB AAABB AAAAA AAAAA AAAAB BBA AAABB</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"base64隐写\"><a href=\"#base64隐写\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"base64隐写\"></a>base64隐写</h2></li>\n<li>CTFCrackTools</li>\n<li>可能是伪加密<h2 id=\"LSB隐写\"><a href=\"#LSB隐写\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"LSB隐写\"></a>LSB隐写</h2></li>\n<li>stegsolve<br>文件用stegsolve打开，Analyse，Date Extract，勾选red blue green3个0，模式选rbg</li>\n<li>kali zsteg<br>zsteg 1.png</li>\n<li>若发现EP后文件头为png则save bin为png文件</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"社会主义核心价值观加密\"><a href=\"#社会主义核心价值观加密\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"社会主义核心价值观加密\"></a>社会主义核心价值观加密</h1><h1 id=\"WireShark\"><a href=\"#WireShark\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"WireShark\"></a>WireShark</h1><ul>\n<li>过滤post请求（登录密码都是post提交）<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">http.request.method==&quot;POST&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"功夫再高也怕菜刀——pcapng文件分析\"><a href=\"#功夫再高也怕菜刀——pcapng文件分析\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"功夫再高也怕菜刀——pcapng文件分析\"></a>功夫再高也怕菜刀——pcapng文件分析</h1></li>\n<li>拿到一个pcapng文件，先binwalk分离一下<br>分离时有压缩包报错了，安装了sasquatch之后成功解压<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">binwalk -eM 6666.pcapng --run-as=root</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>分离之后发现一个压缩包，需要密码<h2 id=\"wireshark分析\"><a href=\"#wireshark分析\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"wireshark分析\"></a>wireshark分析</h2></li>\n<li>输入表达式：<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">http contains &quot;flag&quot; 或者 tcp contains &quot;flag&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>追踪TCP流发现有一个6666.jpg</li>\n<li>分组字节流搜索6666.jpg，并追踪TCP流，找到jpg文件的文件头和文件尾并复制到WinHex</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://starofeden-blog.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/202403231009656.png\" alt=\"d2ef4e90e67e4adcb52ca8aa6d307295\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"Winhex\"><a href=\"#Winhex\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Winhex\"></a>Winhex</h2><ul>\n<li>新建一个文件，剪贴板粘贴选择ASCLL HEX<br>保存为jpg文件打开就可以看到压缩包密码了。</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"ext3-mount挂载文件系统\"><a href=\"#ext3-mount挂载文件系统\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"ext3 - mount挂载文件系统\"></a>ext3 - mount挂载文件系统</h1><p> 通过题目名字得知提供的文件是一个linux文件系统</p>\n<ul>\n<li>搜索flag,找到flag文件位置<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">strings linux | grep flag</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">.flag.txt.swp</span><br><span class=\"line\">flag.txtt.swx</span><br><span class=\"line\">~root/Desktop/file/O7avZhikgKgbF/flag.txt</span><br><span class=\"line\">.flag.txt.swp</span><br><span class=\"line\">flag.txtt.swx</span><br><span class=\"line\">.flag.txt.swp</span><br><span class=\"line\">flag.txtt.swx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>mount挂载文件系统<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo mount linux /mnt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>查看flag文件<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">cat /mnt/O7avZhikgKgbF/flag.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ZmxhZ3tzYWpiY2lienNrampjbmJoc2J2Y2pianN6Y3N6Ymt6an0=</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>base64解密<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">base64 -d /mnt/O7avZhikgKgbF/flag.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"misc图片-做题记录\"><a href=\"#misc图片-做题记录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"misc图片-做题记录\"></a>misc图片-做题记录</h1></li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"pngdebugger\"><a href=\"#pngdebugger\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"pngdebugger\"></a>pngdebugger</h1><blockquote>\n<p>可以来判断图片宽高是否正确 </p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>使用方法：<br>进入Debug目录：<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pngdebugger misc12.png</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"改变图片的宽度？\"><a href=\"#改变图片的宽度？\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"改变图片的宽度？\"></a>改变图片的宽度？</h1><h2 id=\"bmp文件\"><a href=\"#bmp文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"bmp文件\"></a>bmp文件</h2></li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://starofeden-blog.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/202403132137216.png\" alt=\"image-20240313213710084\"></p>\n<p>减去文件头54个字节，最后2个字节，信息块675000个字节<br>文件真实像素为675000 / 3 = 225000<br>除以图片的宽：900 得到高250<br>修改高为：<code>FA 00 00 00</code>   (是小端序噢)</p>\n<h1 id=\"时间戳\"><a href=\"#时间戳\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"时间戳\"></a>时间戳</h1><p>提示：<br><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ctfshow&#123;&#125;, UnixTimestamp, DECtoHEX, getflag</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>把时间戳转十进制（秒）再转十六进制·<code>注意格式</code><br><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">874865822 2699237688 2156662200 460377706</span><br><span class=\"line\">print(hex(874865822)[2:]+hex(2699237688)[2:]+hex(2156662245)[2:]+hex(460377706)[2:])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<h1 id=\"exif\"><a href=\"#exif\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"exif\"></a>exif</h1><ul>\n<li>可以查看到图片的信息<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">exiftool 文件名</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>提示在序列号，是一串数字</li>\n<li>考虑十六进制转ascii文本</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"略缩图隐写（thumbnail隐写）\"><a href=\"#略缩图隐写（thumbnail隐写）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"略缩图隐写（thumbnail隐写）\"></a>略缩图隐写（thumbnail隐写）</h1><ul>\n<li>提示flag在图片里，猜测有两张图片<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">exiftool -ThumbnailImage -b misc22.jpg &gt; 1.jpg</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>另一种方法是FFD8</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"python\"><a href=\"#python\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"python\"></a>python</h1><ul>\n<li>文件处理<br><code>把黑白图片转换成0和1</code><figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> os</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">white = <span class=\"built_in\">open</span>(<span class=\"string\">r&quot;C:\\Users\\xxx\\Desktop\\gif\\0.jpg&quot;</span>,<span class=\"string\">&quot;rb&quot;</span>).read()</span><br><span class=\"line\">black = <span class=\"built_in\">open</span>(<span class=\"string\">r&quot;C:\\Users\\xxx\\Desktop\\gif\\1.jpg&quot;</span>,<span class=\"string\">&quot;rb&quot;</span>).read()</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">binary_flag = <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"built_in\">range</span>(<span class=\"number\">104</span>):</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">with</span> <span class=\"built_in\">open</span>(<span class=\"string\">r&quot;C:\\Users\\xxx\\Desktop\\gif\\%d.jpg&quot;</span>%i,<span class=\"string\">&quot;rb&quot;</span>) <span class=\"keyword\">as</span> f:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> f.read() == white:</span><br><span class=\"line\">            binary_flag += <span class=\"string\">&quot;0&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">else</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">            binary_flag += <span class=\"string\">&quot;1&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">print</span>(binary_flag)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">flag = <span class=\"string\">&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"built_in\">range</span>(<span class=\"built_in\">len</span>(binary_flag)//<span class=\"number\">8</span>):</span><br><span class=\"line\">    flag += <span class=\"built_in\">chr</span>(<span class=\"built_in\">int</span>(binary_flag[i*<span class=\"number\">8</span>:(i+<span class=\"number\">1</span>)*<span class=\"number\">8</span>],<span class=\"number\">2</span>))</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">print</span>(flag)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<blockquote>\n<p>1.使用绝对路径时前面加个r防止转义<br>2.with … as f:<br>3.字符串添加字符：+= “0”<br>4.int(binary_flag[i<em>8:(i+1)</em>8],2):将字符串解析为2进制数字再转换为10进制</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n</ul>\n",
            "tags": []
        }
    ]
}